# The `Call` Struct Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Describes the use of a value in a call instruction, specifying the call&#39;s target, the value&#39;s parameter number, and the possible range of offsets from the beginning of the value that are passed. <a href="#details">More...</a>
